The following files contain Jupyter notebooks implementing the algorithms described in G. Friedland: "Information-Driven Machine Learning: Data Science as an Engineering Discipline", Springer-Nature, December 2023, ISBN: 978-3031394768.

Electronic versions of the book are available here:

English: https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-3-031-39477-5

German: https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-3-031-56274-7

The notebooks have been created from scratch by Neil Patel (NeilP211). They are released under the CC0 license as outlined in LICENSE.
